        </item>
        <item>
            <title>iOS 18 超型广告拦截画面效果，一按广告图片灰飞烟灭</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/07/ios18-safari-distraction-control/tips-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ios18-safari-distraction-control</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/07/ios18-safari-distraction-control/tips-2/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 07:55:04 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iOS App]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPad App]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[MAC App]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[实用技巧]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AdBlock]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iOS 18]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1255030</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">Apple 为 iOS 18、iPadOS 18 和 macOS Sequoia 上的 Safari 浏览器新增了一个名为 Distraction Control 的功能，将容许用户移除浏览器中令人讨厌和分心的 Cookies 提示、广告以及一堆自动播放的影片。</p><figure id="attachment_1255040" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1255040" style="width: 694px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1255040" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/2024080730559-694x421.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="421" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/2024080730559-694x421.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/2024080730559.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1255040" class="wp-caption-text">Screenshot</figcaption></figure><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">I love the new Thanos snap animation in iOS 18 that lets you temporarily remove annoying ads on webpages 🫰 <a href="https://t.co/24UhKxExoy">pic.twitter.com/24UhKxExoy</a></p><p>&mdash; Tom Warren (@tomwarren) <a href="https://twitter.com/tomwarren/status/1820614582991511973?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">August 6, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p style="font-weight: 400;">在 iOS 18 Beta 5 就可以使用到这项功能，但这项功能更偏向为主动式的操作，它不像 Adblock 那一类型的广告拦截器会将广告一律移除，而是需要经过用户的手动操作后才会移除。广告的移除是暂时性而不是永久性，重新载入网站的时候会再次重新显示。根据用户 <a href="https://x.com/tomwarren">@tomwarren</a> 在 X 平台上分享的影片，这个移除广告的效果与《复仇者联盟》系列中的大反派 Thanos 「打响指」的化灰效果十分相似。用户可以在 Safari 浏览器中打开下方的选单，你会发现有一个名为「Hide Distracting Items」的选项，点选后便能点击相关的广告、自动播放影片等会令人分心的烦厌项目并将它们移除（也能用同样的方法将它们重新显示）。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_38060"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/FzBa6Tc-JeE?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>目前这项功能只在开发人员 Beta 版本中推出，但很有可能会在下个月的正式版 iOS 18 中向大家开放这项功能，到时大家就可以一尝扮演 Thanos 的滋味将广告通通化成灰了。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">资料来源：<a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2024/08/05/safari-distraction-control-hands-on/">MacRumors</a></p><p>图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FzBa6Tc-JeE">YouTube @ MacRumors</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/02/ios18-features-that-most-people-missed/life-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】iOS 18 大部分人可能错过的新功能　留言信箱广东话变文字 + 音量键电源键新操作动画</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/07/ios18-allow-audio-playback/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">iOS 18 拍片功能大改进，录影时可继续播音乐毋须 AirPods</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/30/ios18-1-and-ipados18-1-with-apple-intelligence/software/iphone-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple Intelligence 功能首次引入   iOS 18.1 和 iPadOS 18.1 Beta 版推出</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/07/ios18-safari-distraction-control/tips-2/">iOS 18 超型广告拦截画面效果，一按广告图片灰飞烟灭</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/07/ios18-safari-distraction-control/tips-2/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
